dct_title_s: Map of the Province of Canterbury (New Zealand) showing the five routes between the east & west coasts, with sections of the routes, to accompany the paper by Dr. J. Haast
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Routes of exploration are shown by coded colors. Includes 5 elevation profiles of routes: Hurunui Route, Otira Route, North Rakaia Route, Whitcombe Route, and Wanaka Route. From: The Journal of the Royal Geographical Society of London. Vol. 37, (1867), pp. 329-38 held in Firestone Library. Call number: G7 .J687 v.37 1867.
dct_publisher_sm: London: published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle Street, 1867.
